graph TB
    subgraph "Llama Stack K8s Operator"
        Controller[Operator Controller Manager<br/>Deployment]
        LLSDController[LlamaStackDistribution Controller]
        Kustomize[Kustomize-based Deployment Engine]
        FeatureFlags[Feature Flags Manager<br/>ConfigMap]
        ImageMapper[Distribution Image Mapper<br/>ConfigMap]
        NetworkTransformer[Network Policy Transformer<br/>Plugin]

        Controller -->|contains| LLSDController
        LLSDController -->|uses| Kustomize
        LLSDController -->|reads| FeatureFlags
        LLSDController -->|reads| ImageMapper
        Kustomize -->|plugins| NetworkTransformer
    end

    User[User/Developer] -->|creates| LLSDCR[LlamaStackDistribution CR<br/>llamastack.io/v1alpha1]
    LLSDCR -->|watched by| LLSDController

    LLSDController -->|creates| Deployment[Llama Stack Deployment]
    LLSDController -->|creates| Service[Llama Stack Service<br/>ClusterIP 8321/TCP]
    LLSDController -->|creates| PVC[PersistentVolumeClaim<br/>Model Storage]
    LLSDController -->|creates| NetworkPolicy[NetworkPolicy<br/>if enabled]
    LLSDController -->|creates| Ingress[Ingress<br/>if spec.network.exposeRoute=true]

    Deployment -->|uses| PVC
    Service -->|routes to| Deployment
    Ingress -->|exposes| Service

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
        Ollama[Ollama Server]
        vLLM[vLLM Server]
        TGI[TGI Server]
        Registry[Container Registry<br/>docker.io/quay.io]
    end

    LLSDController -->|reconciles via| K8sAPI
    Deployment -->|inference backend| Ollama
    Deployment -->|inference backend| vLLM
    Deployment -->|inference backend| TGI
    Deployment -->|pulls images from| Registry

    subgraph "Internal ODH/RHOAI Integration"
        Prometheus[Prometheus/ServiceMonitor]
        OSMonitoring[OpenShift Monitoring]
        SCC[Security Context Constraints<br/>anyuid]
    end

    Controller -->|exposes metrics to| Prometheus
    Prometheus -->|integrates with| OSMonitoring
    Deployment -->|requires| SCC

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style LLSDController fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style LLSDCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Ollama fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style vLLM fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style TGI fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Registry fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Prometheus fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style OSMonitoring fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style SCC fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
